<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>โปรไฟล์แนะนำตัว - Glass Style</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Kanit', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4158D0 0%, #C850C0 50%, #FFCC70 100%);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .glass-card {
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 25px;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.2);
      color: white;
      max-width: 400px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .glass-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px;
      right: -40px;
      width: 100px;
      height: 100px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .glass-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -50px;
      left: -50px;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .profile-img {
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid #fff;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #eee;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    .social-links {
      margin-top: 25px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      z-index: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    .social-links a {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 22px;
      transition: transform 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
      color: #FFCC70;
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .glass-card {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        max-width: 90%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="glass-card">
    <img class="profile-img" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/300?img=5" alt="Profile Image">
    <h1>สวัสดีครับ ผมชื่อเจ</h1>
    <h2>Web Designer & Front-End Developer</h2>
    <p>
      ผมหลงใหลในการออกแบบเว็บไซต์ที่ดูดี มีสไตล์<br>
      สนุกกับการเขียนโค้ดและสร้างประสบการณ์ผู้ใช้ที่ลื่นไหล<br>
      ชอบกาแฟ ชอบความเรียบง่าย และการพัฒนาตัวเองเสมอ ☕
    </p>
    <div class="social-links">
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
